        "created_at": "2024-07-04T12:45:39.346Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Sometimes it‚Äôs not desirable, but <strong>it‚Äôs critical</strong> <img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/images/emoji/apple/neutral_face.png?v=12\" title=\":neutral_face:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":neutral_face:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"><br>\n<code>Segoe</code> of Windows10x64 is ugly, causing my eyes to bleed.</p>\n<p>If developers don‚Äôt want to add a GUI option, I‚Äôd like to have a ¬´config.json; ephemeral.json¬ª option, something like:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"lang-auto\">\"ui-font\": \"Verdana\"\n\"chat-font\": \"Verdana\"\n</code></pre>\n<p>At least, I have already corrected ¬´ephemeral.json¬ª to <code>\"localeOverride\": \"en-ZA\"</code> for my comfort of datetime perception.</p>",
